- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper proposes a control strategy and derives bounds based on the system dynamics.
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is another possible category as the paper discusses distributed control techniques.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions examples from epidemics spreading, which can be modeled using neural networks.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is unlikely as the paper does not focus on developing new algorithms or data structures.
